data.description: Discover extraordinary 55+ living in this beautifully upgraded and maintained home on Reno's west edge. Built in 2014, this Tahoe model in Sierra Canyon offers 2 bd, 2 ba, and an office/den. The spacious 1,400+ SF open floorplan features granite kitchen countertops, SST appliances, laminate flooring, & primary bedroom bay window. Enjoy the elevated view lot, paver patio with pergola, and low-maintenance landscaping with a golf putting green. This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle! Nestled in the heart of Sierra Canyon, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with extra tall birch cabinets featuring convenient roll-out trays, granite countertops with a matching backsplash, a raised bar, and stainless steel appliances, including a French door refrigerator. The thoughtful touches continue with a frosted glass pantry door, adding a touch of sophistication to the culinary space. Hunter Douglas window coverings throughout and ceiling fans in the living room and primary bedroom enhance the already pleasant atmosphere. The primary bedroom is a retreat with a bay window, providing a cozy nook to relax and unwind. French doors at the office/den add an element of privacy and style. The hall bathroom has been upgraded with an extra-deep tub/shower and a convenient grab bar, ensuring both safety and luxury. The laundry room is fully equipped with a washer, dryer, cabinets, and a sink, making chores a breeze. Step into the backyard oasis, complete with a golf putting green, creating a perfect space for entertainment and relaxation while enjoying views of Peavine Mountain. The front yard beckons you to enjoy the outdoors and Sierra mountain views with a covered porch and accents of beautiful Lodi Gold rock.  Come live the life you've always wanted in this wonderful 55+ Sierra Canyon community!  Amazing amenities include 18,000+sf clubhouse with state of the art fitness center, exercise classes, indoor pool, outdoor hot tub, firepits, expansive patio with spectacular views, indoor walking track, grand lounge, multi-purpose room with catering kitchen, billiards, tennis, pickle ball, bocce ball, miles of paved walking paths, 9-hole golf course, access to driving range and restaurant at Somersett Golf & Country Club, plus limited rounds at a discounted rate at the 18-hole championship course.  All of this plus numerous clubs and groups and an active social calendar means never a dull moment.
